=head1 NAME

C99::CPP::PAST - Abstract syntax tree nodes for C99

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This file implements the various abstract syntax tree nodes
needed for C99.  The currently defined ast nodes:

    C99::CPP::PAST::Node       - base class for all ast nodes

=head1 METHODS

=over 4

=cut

